<p><span class='normal'>&quot;Per Adamsen&quot; &lt;<a href='http://pa@asetek.com'>pa@asetek.com</a>> skrev i en meddelelse </span><br /><span class='normal'><a href='http://news:arll8r$nfe$1@sunsite.dk'>news:arll8r$nfe$1@sunsite.dk</a>... </span><br /><span class='citat'>> Jeg har brug for lidt hj&#230;lp til at &#230;ndre baggrundsfarven i et </span><br /><span class='citat'>> form-felt. Min tanke er, at alt efter hvilken v&#230;rdi felten f&#229;r, </span><br /><span class='citat'>> s&#229; skal felten f&#229; en bestemt baggrundsfarve. </span><br /><span class='citat'>> </span><br /><span class='citat'>> Kan nogen derfor hj&#230;lpe med at fuldende f&#248;lgende linie? </span><br /><span class='citat'>> </span><br /><span class='citat'>> document.myForm.myInput.? = &quot;red&quot;; </span><br /><span class='citat'>> </span><br /><span class='citat'>> P&#229; forh&#229;nd tak! </span><br /><span class='citat'>> </span><br /><span class='citat'>> /Per </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>----- Original Message ----- </span><br /><span class='normal'>From: &quot;Per Adamsen&quot; &lt;<a href='http://pa@asetek.com'>pa@asetek.com</a>> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Newsgroups: dk.edb.internet.webdesign.clientside </span><br /><span class='normal'>Sent: Friday, November 22, 2002 5:16 PM </span><br /><span class='normal'>Subject: Skifte baggrundsfarve i form-felter </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='citat'>> Jeg har brug for lidt hj&#230;lp til at &#230;ndre baggrundsfarven i et </span><br /><span class='citat'>> form-felt. Min tanke er, at alt efter hvilken v&#230;rdi felten f&#229;r, </span><br /><span class='citat'>> s&#229; skal felten f&#229; en bestemt baggrundsfarve. </span><br /><span class='citat'>> </span><br /><span class='citat'>> Kan nogen derfor hj&#230;lpe med at fuldende f&#248;lgende linie? </span><br /><span class='citat'>> </span><br /><span class='citat'>> document.myForm.myInput.? = &quot;red&quot;; </span><br /><span class='citat'>> </span><br /><span class='citat'>> P&#229; forh&#229;nd tak! </span><br /><span class='citat'>> </span><br /><span class='citat'>> /Per </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Hej Per </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Du skal benytte document.myFrom.myInput.style.backgroundColor = &quot;red&quot;; </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Har inkluderet lille eksempel. </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>function changeColor( formElement, value ) { </span><br /><span class='normal'> if ( value == 0 )  { /*Hvis du har mange values/farver benyt case!*/ </span><br /><span class='normal'>  formElement.style.backgroundColor = &quot;red&quot;; </span><br /><span class='normal'> } </span><br /><span class='normal'> else { </span><br /><span class='normal'>  formElement.style.backgroundColor = &quot;blue&quot;; </span><br /><span class='normal'> } </span><br /><span class='normal'>} </span><br /><span class='normal'>&lt;input type=&quot;Text&quot; id=&quot;changeColorElement&quot; onChange=&quot;changeColor( this, </span><br /><span class='normal'>this.value );&quot;> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Venlig Hilsen </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Jacob Winther </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>--- </span><br /><span class='normal'>Outgoing mail is certified Virus Free. </span><br /><span class='normal'>Checked by AVG anti-virus system (<a href='http://www.grisoft.com)'>http://www.grisoft.com)</a>. </span><br /><span class='normal'>Version: 6.0.419 / Virus Database: 235 - Release Date: 13-11-2002 </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'></span><br /></p><hr /><ul class='newslist'><li class='newslist'><a hr